<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٢٧٨٤ - عَنِ مَعْمَرٍ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ الزُّهْرِيِّ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«إِذَا جَهَرَ الْإِمَامُ فَلَا تَقْرَأْ شَيْئًا»</span> عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ،<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>⦗١٣٣⦘<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٢٧٨٥ - عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ، عَنْ قَتَادَةَ مِثْلَهُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>